'''Bihari János''' [{{IPA|ˈbihɒri ˈjaːnoʃ}}] (* 21 deshtonay 1764 ando [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ve%C4%BEk%C3%A9_Blahovo Nagyabony] (adyes [[Slovaiko|Slovayko]]); † 26 Trintonay 1827 ande [[Peshta]]) sas yek Ungarikanô-[[Romane manusha|Rom]] lavutari tay komponist.

== Lesko trajo ==
Lesko dad vi sas lavutari. 1801 voj kerdas leske brave romani banda ande [[Peshta]]. Apal bashavlas ande [[Pozhony]], [[Bech]] thai e intrego [[Ungariya]].

[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ludwig_van_Beethoven Ludwig van Beethoven] thai vi [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Franz_Liszt Franz Liszt] les ashunadine thai les kamline. Liszt phenlas: ''"O bashajipe, lesko varazhitoro lavuta gilyavas, urajlas po amare kan thai rovam..."''([http://books.google.at/books?id=YYyu7HY9dVcC&pg=PA22&lpg=PA22&dq=%22The+tones+sung+by+his+magic+violin+flow+on+our+enchanted+ears+like+the+tears...%22&source=bl&ots=LMYBJoTsIX&sig=Vc5SDT5j-hQv2bsweJhHzTh4pIU&hl=de&ei=kvSmTqfHN7KM4gSAnqDvDw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CDoQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=%22The%20tones%20sung%20by%20his%20magic%20violin%20flow%20on%20our%20enchanted%20ears%20like%20the%20tears...%22&f=false Pagina]).

Bihari bashavlas kaj o [[extrexane-ungarikane krajipe]]. Voj kherdas 85 gilya.

